author: Andrea Park CBS News
title: Photo: Jessa (Duggar) Seewald shows off baby bump
text:
It seems like Jessa (Duggar) Seewald can't wait to have her first baby -- she's been posting pictures of all things babies for weeks now.
Seewald posted a photo of her growing baby bump on Thursday, simply captioning the pic: "36 weeks 4 days." Seewald is very close to her due date of Nov. 1.
Fans are dying to know if Seewald is having a girl or a boy, and she can't stop teasing them.
In another post, Seewald posted a photo of a baby boy outfit and a baby girl outfit and asked her fans to guess the gender of her Baby Seewald.
"Jinger picked out some pretty adorable outfit options for #BabySeewald! Which do you think we'll be putting to use? Right or left?"
Before, Seewald even hinted that she might be having twins, but she seems to have given up on that ruse, referring to the singular "baby" several times. That hasn't stopped her fans from commenting, "Both," on the photo of the two outfits, though.
It looks like we'll find out soon enough: TLC will air a special on Seewald's pregnancy.
36 weeks 4 days
A photo posted by Jessa Seewald (@jessaseewald) on Oct 8, 2015 at 8:32am PDT
